title: প্রকর্ষ-৫৫ (শেবাচিম)
about: We are the 55th batch of Sher-E-Bangla Medical College (SBMC), proudly known as SB 55. With 253 enthusiastic and talented students, we share a commitment to excellence in academics, teamwork, and growth. Together, we aim to uphold the legacy of SBMC and make a meaningful impact in the field of medicine.
